576
00:45:47,119 --> 00:45:48,880
[SPEAKER_02] I sjećam se, sutra dan smo ono.

577
00:45:49,840 --> 00:45:51,679
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam rekla, znači, bila bolje, nemam štake.

578
00:45:51,760 --> 00:45:55,119
