696
00:57:01,519 --> 00:57:02,719
[SPEAKER_02] Negdje ima još možda tjest.

697
00:57:02,960 --> 00:57:05,199
[SPEAKER_02] Kažu, nemam ništa, ani na rado.

698
00:57:06,079 --> 00:57:08,639
